<c.Japanese>早背山</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>わせやま</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>)</c.Japanese>大学教授の<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

