58
00:02:19,433 --> 00:02:20,766
<c.Japanese>ああー！</c.Japanese>

59
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:23,600
<c.Japanese>（狩屋）<c.Japanese>綾</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>あや</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>)</c.Japanese>さん 地元の対応に
