61
00:02:27,333 --> 00:02:29,700
<c.Japanese>ここまでバカだとは</c.Japanese>

62
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,466
<c.Japanese>学費返せ！</c.Japanese>

63
00:02:33,300 --> 00:02:34,166
<c.Japanese>（貝原）翔くん</c.Japanese>

64
