108
00:04:27,166 --> 00:04:28,700
<c.Japanese>総理はお前だ！</c.Japanese>

109
00:04:30,866 --> 00:04:32,233
<c.Japanese>誰のせいで<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

