134
00:06:17,233 --> 00:06:19,400
<c.Japanese>翔くんかと思ったけど<c.Japanese>—</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>

135
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,366
<c.Japanese>気のせいか</c.Japanese>

136
00:06:29,300 --> 00:06:30,466
